            "id": 78785,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Aprendamos cómo mostrar diferentes tipos de valores juntos en la consola con una función útil conocida como cadenas formateadas.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Adding strings",
            "id": 78795,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Hemos aprendido que podemos usar <code>+</code> para sumar dos cadenas y mostrarlas juntas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;new&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"&quot; messages&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"12\" endIndex=\"13\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"new messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>+</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Adding numbers and strings",
            "id": 78796,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Pero usar <code>+</code> para combinar datos numéricos como <code>2</code> y <code>\" new messages\"</code> juntos produce un <strong>error</strong> ya que son diferentes tipos de valores.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"&quot; new messages&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"9\" /><option startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"25\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Traceback (most recent call last):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  File &quot;/home/default/code/file.py&quot;, line 1, in &lt;module&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(2 + &quot; new messages&quot;)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"TypeError: unsupported operand type(s) for +: 'int' and 'str'\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>+</code> seguido de <code>\" new messages\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Formatted strings",
            "id": 78797,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Las f-strings, abreviatura de cadenas formateadas, nos permiten mostrar expresiones como agregar una cadena a un número, sin ningún error.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" new messages&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"25\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2 new messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>f\"{2} new messages\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Formatted strings",
            "id": 78798,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Cada declaración de f-string consta de dos partes, primero el carácter <code>f</code>, luego la cadena que queremos formatear.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"6\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" new messages&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"7\" /><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"25\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6 new messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>f</code> seguido de <code>\"{6} new messages\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Formatted strings",
            "id": 78799,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A continuación, añadimos el diferente tipo de valor entre llaves para que se muestre como una sola declaración de impresión. Como aquí, con <code>{2}</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" new messages&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"11\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2 new messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>{2}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Formatted strings",
            "id": 78800,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Insertar variables como <code>new_messages</code> entre las llaves también muestra su valor.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"new_messages = \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{new_messages}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" new messages&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"38\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"2\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2 new messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>new_messages</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Expressions",
            "id": 80749,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>También podemos usar expresiones como <code>new - read</code> entre las llaves para mostrar su valor.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"new = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"read = \" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{new - read}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" unread messages&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"37\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"3 unread messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>new - read</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Formatted strings",
            "id": 78802,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos usar llaves para insertar valores tantas veces como queramos dentro del f-string. Míralo aquí con <code>5</code>, y luego con <code>2</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" new messages and \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"2\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" friend requests&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"10\" /><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"31\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5 new messages and 2 friend requests\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>5</code> seguido de <code>2</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Formatted strings",
            "id": 82107,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para reutilizar un f-string, podemos guardarlo en una variable, como aquí con <code>status</code> y <code>f\"{new} new messages\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"new = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{new}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" new messages&quot;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(status)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5 new messages\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>status</code> seguido de <code>=</code> y finalmente <code>f\"{new} new messages\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
