            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Muestra la temperatura actual codificando <code>degrees</code> entre llaves.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"degrees = \" /><text value=\"70\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Temperature: \" /><text value=\"{degrees}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"F&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"42\" /><option startIndex=\"42\" endIndex=\"43\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Temperature: 70F\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>{</code> seguido de <code>degrees</code> y finalmente <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
